sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Inference as Ollama/vLLM<br/>11434/8000 TCP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Kustomize: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification (in-process)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Get LlamaStackDistribution<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Kustomize: Render manifests (in-process)
    Kustomize-->>Controller: Generated Kubernetes resources
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resources<br/>(Deployment, Service, HPA, etc.)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR Status: Ready

    Note over Client,Inference: Flow 3: Llama Stack Inference Request

    Client->>LlamaStack: POST /inference/chat<br/>Optional TLS 1.3<br/>None/Custom Auth
    LlamaStack->>Inference: Inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional Token
    Inference->>Inference: GPU/CPU Processing
    Inference-->>LlamaStack: Inference result
    LlamaStack-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Prometheus,Proxy: Flow 2: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS TLS<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: Token Review<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Token Valid
    Proxy->>Controller: Fetch metrics<br/>HTTP/8080
    Controller-->>Proxy: Prometheus metrics
    Proxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics response

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: ConfigMap Update and Pod Restart

    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification (in-process)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment<br/>Add pod template annotation<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>LlamaStack: Rolling restart (Kubernetes-managed)
    LlamaStack-->>K8sAPI: New pods ready
